OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781100698
OL,3,CSo-called 'Tourism Tax' rejected by
OL,4,CDumfries and Galloway councillors
OL,6,FPlans to charge visitors extra for
OL,7,Fovernight stays in Dumfries and
OL,8,FGalloway have been rejected after
OL,9,Fcouncillors voted against taking
OL,10,Fforward proposals for a tourist tax.
OL,12,FThe visitor levy, otherwise known as a
OL,13,Ftourist tax, would have added an extra
OL,14,Fcharge to overnight stays in our
OL,15,Fregion, with the money being used to
OL,16,Ffund key infrastructure improvements
OL,17,Fsuch as roads, parks, public toilets,
OL,18,Fand helping to advertise the region to
OL,19,Ftourists.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
