PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781100698
OL,3,CSo-called 'Tourism Tax' rejected by
OL,4,CDumfries and Galloway councillors
OL,6,FThe proposal was considered after new
OL,7,Fpowers were granted to Scottish
OL,8,Fcouncils under the Visitor Levy
OL,9,F(Scotland) Act. A report to
OL,10,Fcouncillors highlighted pressure on
OL,11,Flocal services and infrastructure
OL,12,Flinked to tourism, but also found
OL,13,Fstrong opposition to the levy,
OL,14,Fparticularly among tourism businesses.
OL,16,FMore than 1,650 responses were
OL,17,Fgathered during an engagement exercise
OL,18,Fwith residents, visitors and
OL,19,Fbusinesses ahead of Tuesday's (9 June)
OL,20,Fmeeting.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
