CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1781100698
OL,3,CSo-called 'Tourism Tax' rejected by
OL,4,CDumfries and Galloway councillors
OL,6,FCouncillors were asked whether to move
OL,7,Fforward with a formal consultation on
OL,8,Fa proposed scheme. However, members
OL,9,Fvoted not to progress the plans,
OL,10,Fbringing work on a visitor levy to an
OL,11,Fend.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/3
